{"comments":"TextShadow molecule — shadow effect for text elements.\n\n## CSS text-shadow\n\nUnlike box-shadow, text-shadow:\n- Has NO spread radius\n- Has NO inset option\n- Follows the glyph contours precisely\n- Can be layered (comma-separated)\n\nFormat: `text-shadow: <offset-x> <offset-y> <blur-radius> <color>;`\n\n## Usage\n\n```purescript\nimport Hydrogen.Schema.Elevation.TextShadow as TS\nimport Hydrogen.Schema.Color.RGB as RGB\n\n-- Create a text shadow\nglow :: TS.TextShadow\nglow = TS.textShadow\n  { offsetX: 0.0\n  , offsetY: 0.0\n  , blur: 10.0\n  , color: RGB.rgba 59 130 246 80  -- blue glow\n  }\n\n-- Layered shadows for 3D effect\nembossed :: TS.LayeredTextShadow\nembossed = TS.layeredText\n  [ TS.textShadow { offsetX: 1.0, offsetY: 1.0, blur: 0.0\n                  , color: RGB.rgba 255 255 255 50 }  -- highlight\n  , TS.textShadow { offsetX: -1.0, offsetY: -1.0, blur: 0.0\n                  , color: RGB.rgba 0 0 0 30 }  -- shadow\n  ]\n\n-- Convert to CSS\ncss = TS.toLegacyCss glow  -- \"0px 0px 10px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.8)\"\n```\n","declarations":[{"children":[],"comments":"Text shadow — parameters for CSS text-shadow.\n\nAll measurements in CSS pixels.\n","info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"typeSynonym","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Record"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["offsetX",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["offsetY",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["blur",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["color",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","RGB"],"RGBA"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"tag":"REmpty"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[118,4],"name":"../../hydrogen/s